{"tid":909584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那警破假安全套生產集團 檢50萬盒假杜蕾斯、岡本","createTime":"2018-11-20T13:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T02:10:11.000Z","uid":71543,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"13a35ebb145e6f57707118f568783f494984257d","tid":909584,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"搶完奶粉 連condom都要黎香港搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/condom-01_XsLq4_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcondom-01_XsLq4_1200x0.png&h=b0bf44b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫州蒼南警方經過半年調查，搗破一個假安全套生產集團，拘捕 17 人，檢獲超過 50 萬盒假安全套，包括杜蕾斯、岡本等名牌，集團主腦透露，市面上的正版安全套每盒售20 至 150 人民幣，他們生產的假貨成本一盒只是 0.5 元人民幣，批發價只是 1 到 2 元，批發賣到河北、河南、浙江、福建、湖北等 28 個省市，在中小型賓館、超市、便利店，和自動販賣機等，以正貨價格出售。<br />\n<br />\n據內地傳媒報道，警方先是鎖定一個39歲姓林的溫州人，之後陸續發現12個生產加工場和貨倉，拘捕17人，姓林的疑犯透露他們在不夠半年時間，生產了超過100萬盒假安全套，獲利30多萬，他們是從深圳等地一些工廠，低價買入劣質安全套，但送到位於農村的偏僻加工點，聘請農民工加工包裝，包括淋上低質素的矽油作潤滑劑之後出售。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，假安全套外表和真貨品十分相似，消費者難以辨別真假，但材料質素差，衛生不達標，會影響用者健康，涉案被捕17人，因涉嫌生產、銷售偽劣產品罪，正被拘留。"},{"pid":"6839aac9f484c319f264dae3a3c1523d22814d4f","tid":909584,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"衛生不達標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用完生性病"},{"pid":"df66d82ae9813e6a1b1d3240ecc771ab384a8156","tid":909584,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"哇屌<br />\n好大機會香港D藥房都係賣哂呢D"},{"pid":"4ba5b4bc2887f5c40979b623c34741b5e3a3dedc","tid":909584,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"雙11 熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaceb8ae94c57cd934c9a4214e607c101488182","tid":909584,"uid":61257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"雙11熱賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e91bc52b79d87f548f971ee822d6ffbdbbe565","tid":909584,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"大陸假野仲要賣正貨價 爽呀"},{"pid":"842b31c2b43b48f6e848e5293c712f50e769ff74","tid":909584,"uid":4876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"連超市 便利店都入假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f40ab7a6f799698f64e912b4a08f6cc97dd730","tid":909584,"uid":120678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"痴撚線condom都有假<br />\n支那人扑野都要提心吊膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0e169dffd6a8f4adaf2bde427aecc9561cc57f","tid":909584,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會爆炸"},{"pid":"ea0656bbe4ae6422cdef603743176116b2b0f3e9","tid":909584,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57f40ab7a6f799698f64e912b4a08f6cc97dd730","tid":909584,"uid":120678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"痴撚線condom都有假<br />\n支那人扑野都要提心吊膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcc540a0c04a710046c53da4dae6d62dfcbf621","tid":909584,"uid":175655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"好彩我從來唔用套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad0fd1050a072f0373dacbb12a492f7c2ad708d","tid":909584,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"好心啦&hellip; 咁都要造假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid